      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see what u mean about candidate a. but what about candidate b's leadership stuff with the community organizing? surely that requires a lot of grit and managing people under pressure? it feels like and maybe im being biased here, but u seem to be saying candidate b might not be as \"intense\" or \"professional\" just because their activities are different. why does rowing/debate translate to corporate fit better than community work does?",
